@@ -35,7 +35,11 @@   - Hardware Longevity
   - Ecosystem of Respectful Apps
 - Principles
   - Based on the original Software Freedom definition, GNOME's focus on inclusivity and maintainability, the local-first research from Ink & Switch and the holistic lifecycle view from Permacomputing
-  - Software Freedom
+  - Software Freedom (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Free_Software_Definition#/media/File:4_Essential_Freedoms_of_Software.png)
+    - Run the software whenver you wish, for whatever purpose
+    - Study the source code and make modifications to the software
+    - Give or sell copies of the software
+    - Give or sell copies of your modified versions
   - Built For Everyone
   - Design-First
   - Vertical Integration

